{"tid":1099286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子不滿新髮型　反按髮型師在椅上剃頭報復","createTime":"2019-04-09T16:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T16:59:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59f08bd94876cc89623dec679c553a6449ed5087","tid":1099286,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190408/photo/bkn-20190408211151907-0408_00952_001_01b.jpg?20190408230524\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190408211151907-0408_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20190408230524&h=7b09d938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶一名陳姓男子上月底到一間理髮店剪頭髮後，因不滿自己的髮型，於是與髮型師發生口角爭執。期間陳男把對方按在椅上，更把髮型師的頭髮亂剃一通作報復，然後憤而離開理髮店。事後陳已被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n身穿藍衣的陳男，上月31日到南岸一間理髮店剪頭髮。不料理髮過後不滿髮型師的「作品」，憤而與對方理論。後來陳男一時之氣下，把對方推到座位上，更把他按住不放。雖然髮型師極力掙扎，惟最終還是被陳男捉回椅上。<br />\n<br />\n未料，陳男突然手執剃髮器在對方頭上亂剃一通。由於髮型師力氣不及陳男，故只好一臉無奈地坐在椅上，任陳男魚肉。最後陳男「報復」成功後，便憤而離去。"},{"pid":"95e872b04851c0c58f7247dcfe7e34a723b5e52c","tid":1099286,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0eHphA2Syvk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0eHphA2Syvk&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=466e6a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0eHphA2Syvk</a>"},{"pid":"a403e94a35c36361d87fcc6e394bfdd86f5343e1","tid":1099286,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc31d76a64d728df705d99044a526012efe6d603","tid":1099286,"uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.mic.com/ZDM1N2ViYmQ2NCMvdHMxWFJEMVhkN3ZMZXdwQXI1ekZBSTFYU0VnPS9maXQtaW4vNzYweDAvZmlsdGVyczpub191